ni attivisti&#8221; &#8211; <a href=\"https://www.meetup.com/it-IT/wordpress-meetup-milano/events/295043036/\">iscriviti qui per partecipare</a></p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Verona</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>lun 18 set, ore 19:00 &#8220;Multipagina, one page o landing page?&#8221; &#8211; <a href=\"https://www.meetup.com/treviso-wordpress-meetup/events/294758493\">iscriviti qui per </a><a href=\"https://www.meetup.com/it-IT/verona-wordpress-meetup/events/295885114/\">p</a><a href=\"https://www.meetup.com/treviso-wordpress-meetup/events/294758493\">artecipare</a></p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Pisa</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>mar 19 set, ore 18:00 &#8220;WordPress e l&#8217;utilizzo dell&#8217;editor a blocchi (Gutenberg)&#8221; &#8211; <a href=\"https://www.meetup.com/it-IT/pisa-wordpress-meetup/events/295173372/\" data-type=\"link\" data-id=\"https://www.meetup.com/it-IT/pisa-wordpress-meetup/events/295173372/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">iscriviti qui per partecipare</a></p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Genova</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>mer 20 set, ore 18:30 &#8220;WP4ME: Valentina Olini, Web Designer Freelance, ci racconter la sua esperienza&#8221; &#8211; <a href=\"https://www.meetup.com/it-IT/wordpress-meetup-genova/events/295971799/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">iscriviti qui per partecipare</a></p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Napoli</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>mer 20 set, ore 19:00 &#8220;Blocks:verso il Full Site Editing e oltre!&#8221; &#8211; <a href=\"https://www.meetup.com/it-IT/wordpress-napoli-meetup/events/295262049/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">iscriviti qui per partecipare</a></p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Torino</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>gio 21 set, ore 18:30 &#8220;La mia cassetta per gli attrezzi: plugin e tool&#8221; &#8211; <a href=\"https://www.meetup.com/it-IT/wordpress-meetup-torino/events/295779110/\">iscriviti qui per partecipare</a></p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Roma</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>ven 22 set, ore 18:00 &#8220;Perch utilizzare un sito di staging&#8221; &#8211; <a href=\"https://www.meetup.com/it-IT/romawordpress/events/295718967/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">iscriviti qui per partecipare</a></p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Vicenza</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>mar 26 set, ore 19:00 &#8220;Ask Me Anything&#8221; &#8211; <a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https://www.meetup.com/it-IT/wordpress-meetup-vicenza/events/295924612/\" target=\"_blank\">iscriviti qui per partecipare</a></p>\n\n\n\n<div style=\"height:100px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:86:\"https://it.wordpress.org/news/2023/09/tutti-i-meetup-di-settembre-2023-in-italia/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:3;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:91:\"\n		\n		\n					\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n\n					\n										\n					\n					\n			\n		\n		\n			\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:39:\"Tutti i Meetup di luglio 2023 in Italia\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:78:\"https://it.wordpress.org/news/2023/07/tutti-i-meetup-di-luglio-2023-in-italia/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s: