bsp;<a href=\"https://it.wordpress.org/meetup/\">elencati qui.</a></p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Nei prossimi giorni si incontrano le community di:</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Milano</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>mer 05 apr, ore 19:00 &#8220;Come creare Temi Child per WordPress&#8221; &#8211; <a href=\"https://www.meetup.com/wordpress-meetup-milano/events/292550309\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">iscriviti qui per partecipare</a></p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Lecce</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>gio 06 apr, ore 18:00 &#8220;eCommerce da zero a hero: come avviare uno shop di successo&#8221; &#8211; <a href=\"https://www.meetup.com/wordpress-meetup-lecce/events/292275298/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">iscriviti qui per partecipare</a></p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Verona</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>lun 17 apr, ore 19:00 &#8220;WordPress Meetup Verona #54: L&#8217;importanza del personal branding&#8221; &#8211; <a href=\"https://www.meetup.com/Verona-WordPress-Meetup/events/292724756\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">iscriviti qui per partecipare</a></p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Olbia</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>mer 19 apr, ore 17:00 &#8220;Impariamo a usare l&#8217;editor di WordPress per pubblicare su internet&#8221; &#8211; <a href=\"https://www.meetup.com/it-IT/olbia-wordpress-meetup/events/292437552/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">iscriviti qui per partecipare</a></p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Genova</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>mer 19 apr, ore 18:30 &#8220;Community WordPress: special guest Isotta Peira&#8221; &#8211; <a href=\"https://www.meetup.com/it-IT/wordpress-meetup-genova/events/292210223/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">iscriviti qui per partecipare</a></p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Roma</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>ven 21 apr, ore 18:00 &#8220;Tutto quello che volevi sapere su ChatGPT&#8221; &#8211; <a href=\"https://www.meetup.com/RomaWordPress/events/292321068\" target=\"_blank\" 