2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Verona</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>lun 19 giu, ore 19:00 &#8220;Ask me anything&#8221; &#8211; <a href=\"https://www.meetup.com/it-IT/verona-wordpress-meetup/events/293955944/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">iscriviti qui per partecipare</a></p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Genova</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>mer 21 giu, ore 18:30 &#8220;WCEU Report &#8211; Woocommerce do e donts&#8221; &#8211; <a href=\"https://www.meetup.com/wordpress-meetup-genova/events/294286255/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">iscriviti qui per partecipare</a></p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Treviso</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>gio 22 giu, ore 19:30 &#8220;Sfruttare il potenziale dei Custom Post Types e delle Tassonomie&#8221; &#8211; <a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https://www.meetup.com/it-IT/treviso-wordpress-meetup/events/293155825/\" target=\"_blank\">iscriviti qui per partecipare</a></p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Roma</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>ven 23 giu, ore 18:00 &#8220;WordPress Multisite: un network di siti da una sola installazione&#8221; &#8211; <a href=\"https://www.meetup.com/it-IT/romawordpress/events/291472496/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">iscriviti qui per partecipare</a></p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Napoli</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>mer 28 giu, ore 19:00 &#8220;I blocchi pattern di WordPress&#8221; &#8211; <a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https://www.meetup.com/wordpress-napoli-meetup/events/294300946/\" target=\"_blank\">iscriviti qui per partecipare</a></p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Terni</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>mer 28 giu, ore 19:00 &#8220;WP Multisite, un network con una sola installazione!&#8221; &#8211; <a href=\"https://www.meetup.com/it-IT/wordpress-meetup-terni/events/294223650/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">iscriviti qui per partecipare</a></p>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity is-style-dots\" style=\"margin-top:33px;margin-bottom:33px\" />\n\n\n