press.org/dhanendran/\' class=\'mention\'><span class=\'mentions-prefix\'>@</span>dhanendran</a> <a href=\'https://profiles.wordpress.org/kaderibrahim/\' class=\'mention\'><span class=\'mentions-prefix\'>@</span>kaderibrahim</a> Aymenboch</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Un ringraziamento anche a <a href=\'https://profiles.wordpress.org/webtechpooja/\' class=\'mention\'><span class=\'mentions-prefix\'>@</span>webtechpooja</a> <a href=\'https://profiles.wordpress.org/courtneypk/\' class=\'mention\'><span class=\'mentions-prefix\'>@</span>courtneypk</a> <a href=\'https://profiles.wordpress.org/meaganhanes/\' class=\'mention\'><span class=\'mentions-prefix\'>@</span>meaganhanes</a> che hanno contribuito a questo post.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>#localization</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:95:\"https://it.wordpress.org/news/2023/05/riassunto-progetto-content-localization-foundations/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"1\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:7;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:109:\"\n		\n		\n					\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n\n					\n										\n					\n					\n			\n		\n		\n			\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:21:\"Meetup di Maggio 2023\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:60:\"https://it.wordpress.org/news/2023/05/meetup-di-maggio-2023/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s: