\"https://it.wordpress.org/meetup/\">elencati qui.</a></p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Nei prossimi giorni si incontrano le community di:</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Milano</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>mer 05 apr, ore 19:00 &#8220;Come creare Temi Child per WordPress&#8221; &#8211; <a href=\"https://www.meetup.com/wordpress-meetup-milano/events/292550309\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">iscriviti qui per partecipare</a></p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Lecce</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>gio 06 apr, ore 18:00 &#8220;eCommerce da zero a hero: come avviare uno shop di successo&#8221; &#8211; <a href=\"https://www.meetup.com/wordpress-meetup-lecce/events/292275298/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">iscriviti qui per partecipare</a></p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Verona</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>lun 17 apr, ore 19:00 &#8220;WordPress Meetup Verona #54: L&#8217;importanza del personal branding&#8221; &#8211; <a href=\"https://www.meetup.com/Verona-WordPress-Meetup/events/292724756\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">iscriviti qui per partecipare</a></p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Olbia</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>mer 19 apr, ore 17:00 &#8220;Impariamo a usare l&#8217;editor di WordPress per pubblicare su internet&#8221; &#8211; <a href=\"https://www.meetup.com/it-IT/olbia-wordpress-meetup/events/292437552/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">iscriviti qui per partecipare</a></p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Genova</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>mer 19 apr, ore 18:30 &#8220;Community WordPress: special guest Isotta Peira&#8221; &#8211; <a href=\"https://www.meetup.com/it-IT/wordpress-meetup-genova/events/292210223/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">iscriviti qui per partecipare</a></p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Roma</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>ven 21 apr, ore 18:00 &#8220;Tutto quello che volevi sapere su ChatGPT&#8221; &#8211; <a href=\"https://www.meetup.com/RomaWordPress/events/292321068\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">iscriviti qui per partecipare</a></p>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity is-style-dots\" style=\"margin-top:33px;margin-bottom:33px\" />\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center is-style-serif has-blueberry-3-background-color has-background\">&#8230; articolo  in  aggiornamento: saranno aggiunte altre date di altri meetup, torna a leggere questo articolo nei prossimi giorni&#8230;</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:65:\"https://it.wordpress.org/news/2023/04/meetup-di-aprile-2023/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}}}s:27:\"http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom\";a:1:{s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:0:\"\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:3:{s:4:\"href\";s:30:\"https://it.wordpress.org/feed/\";s:3:\"rel\";s:4:\"self\";s:4:\"type\";s:19:\"application/rss+xml\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:44:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/syndication/\";a:2:{s:12:\"updatePeriod\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:9:\"\n	hourly	\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:15:\"updateFrequency\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:4:\"\n	1	\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}}}}}}}}s:4:\"type\";i:128;s:7:\"headers\";O:48:\"WpOrg\\Requests\\Utility\\CaseInsensitiveDictionary\":1:{s:7:\"\0*\0data\";a:10:{s:6:\"server\";s:5:\"nginx\";s:4:\"date\";s:29:\"Mon, 16 Oct 2023 17:23:15 GMT\";s